cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  This CITATION.cff describes how to cite THIS publication index repository.
  To cite an individual paper, please use that paper's own BibTeX entry found in
  publications/<paper-folder>/bibtex.bib instead.
title: "Mamdouh Muhammad - Academic Publications Index"
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Muhammad
    given-names: Mamdouh
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0009-9685-8880"
    affiliation: "Friedrich-Alexander-Universitat Erlangen-Nurnberg (FAU)"
abstract: >-
  A central index and archive of the academic publications of Mamdouh Muhammad in the
  area of AI-based cybersecurity for smart grids, intrusion detection systems, industrial
  control systems, Modbus/TCP security, flow-based IDS, LLM-assisted IDS, dataset bias,
  reproducibility, and SDN security. This repository stores metadata, BibTeX, links, and
  reproducibility notes; it does not host publisher PDFs.
keywords:
  - cybersecurity
  - smart grids
  - intrusion detection systems
  - industrial control systems
  - Modbus/TCP
  - flow-based IDS
  - LLM-assisted security
  - dataset bias
  - reproducibility
  - SDN security
license: CC-BY-4.0  # applies to this index's text/metadata; see LICENSE for the mixed-content notice
repository-code: "https://github.com/MamdouhEgy/mamdouh-publications"
date-released: "2026-06-15"
